hainlink-system--accordion chainlink-system--cc-single"><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-top"><div class="chainlink-system--u-hflex-between-center chainlink-system--u-gap-16"><h3 class="chainlink-system--accordion-question">Decentralized network infrastructure</h3><div class="chainlink-system--u-icon chainlink-system--cc-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><line x1="12" y1="4" x2="12" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="chainlink-system--plus-vert"></line><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="chainlink-system--plus-horiz"></line></svg></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-line"></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-bottom"><div class="chainlink-system--u-pt-4 chainlink-system--u-pb-16"><p>The Chainlink data standard provides onchain applications with access to secure and reliable data from offchain sources.</p></div></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion chainlink-system--cc-single"><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-top"><div class="chainlink-system--u-hflex-between-center chainlink-system--u-gap-16"><h3 class="chainlink-system--accordion-question">Secure and reliable data onchain</h3><div class="chainlink-system--u-icon chainlink-system--cc-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><line x1="12" y1="4" x2="12" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="chainlink-system--plus-vert"></line><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="chainlink-system--plus-horiz"></line></svg></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-line"></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-bottom"><div class="chainlink-system--u-pt-4 chainlink-system--u-pb-16"><p>High-integrity, tamper-resistant data powers financial applications and tokenized assets across onchain markets.</p></div></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion chainlink-system--cc-single"><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-top"><div class="chainlink-system--u-hflex-between-center chainlink-system--u-gap-16"><h3 class="chainlink-system--accordion-question">Seamless interoperability across networks</h3><div class="chainlink-system--u-icon chainlink-system--cc-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><line x1="12" y1="4" x2="12" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="chainlink-system--plus-vert"></line><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="chainlink-system--plus-horiz"></line></svg></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-line"></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-bottom"><div class="chainlink-system--u-pt-4 chainlink-system--u-pb-16"><p>Secure cross-chain messaging and token transfers bridge ecosystems and connect legacy infrastructure.</p></div></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion chainlink-system--cc-single"><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-top"><div class="chainlink-system--u-hflex-between-center chainlink-system--u-gap-16"><h3 class="chainlink-system--accordion-question">Built-in automated compliance</h3><div class="chainlink-system--u-icon chainlink-system--cc-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><line x1="12" y1="4" x2="12" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="chainlink-system--plus-vert"></line><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="chainlink-system--plus-horiz"></line></svg></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-line"></div></div><div class="chainlink-system--accordion-bottom"><div class="chainlink-system--u-pt-4 chainlink-system--u-pb-16"><p>Modular services simplify identity management, policy enforcement, and reporting for compliance-focused digital assets.</p></div></div></div><div class="cha